name: Inferno Maw Chillchest
text: In the twilight glen, the Chillchest roared—a fiery hunger within its iron belly. Villagers whispered tales of its insatiable appetite, feeding it offerings of frost-kissed fruits to quell its smoldering wrath. Each night, it stood sentinel, a blazing guardian against the creeping cold of the encroaching darkness.
